Titolo: Captain Bible in Dome of Darkness

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: Captain Bible in Dome of Darkness is a Christian video game title released by Bridgestone Multimedia Group in 1994. The main focus of the game is scripture memorization but action video game elements can also play a significant role depending on options selected during setup.
While the "original version" of the software is not available legally for free, a stripped-down 'Special Edition' remains available as a free download from a variety of sites.

